title: Richard Scarry's Best Busy People Video Ever!
description: This entry from Richard Scarry's charming animated series introduces kids to the workplace, exploring different types of jobs that adults have and examining how their work affects the rest of society. Inspired by their teacher's latest lesson, Huckle, Rhonda Raccoon, Lowly Worm and the rest of the gang play an imaginative round of "grown-up," where each of them takes on the job they'd like to have in the future.
